Windlords missiles both miss the massive Gemini Dragon as he flys 
over the Chivtron base. The dragon laughs evily as it looks down at 
Nightlight and Starstop and then turns it's attentin to the base 
itself. A moment later the right head launchs four explosive 
fireballs at the base as it fires a continue freeze beam at another 
part.
